00:09:44.360 --> 00:09:45.200
If you can stand,

00:09:46.390 --> 00:09:47.240
so can I.

00:09:53.960 --> 00:09:54.800
Sister,

00:09:55.630 --> 00:09:56.510
are you alright?

00:10:00.840 --> 00:10:02.390
